defaultGiven the several existing obligations on English Heritage that cover the same territory as the proposed duty, we are concerned by the potential for confusion as to how compliance with each should be achieved and of overlapping reporting requirements. We would be very keen to see consolidation of guidance and reporting obligations as far as possible. 
