default19. How is a duty to have regard to the desirability of economic growth likely to affect those regulators to which it is applied? 
default&#xa0;
default              
defaultWe believe it will impact where there is more than one way of achieving satisfactory compliance. In such circumstances it is obviously important to understand which means of regulation would be the least burdensome and the most supportive of growth. 
default&#xa0;
default              
defaultAs commented above, understanding the impact of heritage guidance is fundamental to achieving successful conservation. It is also part of existing compliance and reporting regimes to which English Heritage is subject. 
default&#xa0;
